The Legend of Bagger Vance;;2000;;PG-13;;Drama,Fantasy,Sport;;6.7;;Robert Redford;;Will Smith,Matt Damon,Charlize Theron,Bruce McGill,Joel Gretsch,J. Michael Moncrief,Peter Gerety,Lane Smith,Michael O'Neill,Thomas Jay Ryan,Trip Hamilton,Dermot Crowley,Harve Presnell,Danny Nelson,Bob Penny,Michael McCarty,Carrie Preston,Turner Green;;A disillusioned war veteran, Captain Rannulph Junuh, reluctantly agrees to play a game of golf. He finds the game futile until his caddy, Bagger Vance, teaches him the secret of the authentic golf stroke which turns out also to be the secret to mastering any challenge and finding meaning in life.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0146984/